        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/32724679/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/32724679/" class="">第12页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1214713/" class=" " title="暖暖的烟雨迷蒙">暖暖的烟雨迷蒙</a>
                (就是根葱)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="32724679">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">柯律芝总统致美国人民的祝词手迹：''圣诞节不是时间，不是季节，而是心灵的世界'' 其实适用于每一个节日

Christmas is not a time nor a season, but a state of mind. To cherish peace and goodwill, to be plenteous in mercy, is to have the real spirit of Christmas.

- Calvin Coolidge</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-08-31 16:11</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>柯律芝总统致美国人民的祝词手迹：''圣诞节不是时间，不是季节，而是心灵的世界''</q></blockquote> 其实适用于每一个节日<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Christmas is not a time nor a season, but a state of mind. To cherish peace and goodwill, to be plenteous in mercy, is to have the real spirit of Christmas.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>- Calvin Coolidge
